data.chText: （同类物丛生或聚集的）簇，团，束，串
data.enText: a group of things of the same type that grow or appear close together
The plant bears its flowers in clusters.
a leukaemia cluster (= an area where there are more cases of the disease than you would expect)
a group of people, animals or things close together
a group of consonants which come together in a word or phrase, for example /str/ at the beginning of string
to come together in a small group or groups

data.chText: 孩子们聚集在房间的角落里。
data.enText: The children clustered together in the corner of the room.

data.chText: 医生焦急地围在他的床边。
data.enText: The doctors clustered anxiously around his bed.

means: (同类物丛生或聚集的)簇，团，束，串

ex.chText: 一条小溪从树丛中蜿蜒流过。
ex.enText: A stream meanders gently through a clump of trees.

ex.chText: 就走到转弯处那丛桦树那儿。
ex.enText: Just walk to that clump of birches at the turn.

synonyms.bx: 指长在一起的树木、灌木或其他植物。

ex.chText: 她采了一大捧花来装饰房间。
ex.enText: She picked a large bunch of flowers to decorate her room.

ex.chText: 他用五个土豆换得一串香蕉。
ex.enText: He traded five potatoes for a bunch of bananas.

synonyms.bx: 指束、绑或长在一起的事物。

ex.chText: 丽塔开始翻看她收到的一扎信件。
ex.enText: Rita started to go through the bundle of letters that she received.

ex.chText: 他把一捆旧杂志卖给了二手书店。
ex.enText: He sold a bundle of old magazines to the second-hand bookstore.

synonyms.bx: 指包或捆在一起的纸张、衣服、木棍等。

ex.chText: 他突然看见了一簇红莓。
ex.enText: He suddenly saw a cluster of red berries.

ex.chText: 从这儿你能看到一片低矮的农舍。
ex.enText: You can see a cluster of low farmhouses from here.
A cluster of children stood behind him.

synonyms.bx: 指丛生的或聚集在一起的同类事物，如动植物、人、建筑等。

tr: a grouping of a number of similar things
gather or cause to gather into a cluster
example: She bunched her fingers into a fist

tr: come together as in a cluster or flock
example: The poets constellate in this town every summer

value.def: A cluster of people or things is a small group of them close together.

example.tran: 一群群身着正装的男人

example.ex: There's no town here, just a cluster of shops, cabins and motels at the side of the highway.
example.tran: 这儿没有城镇，只在公路边上有一片商店、小木屋和汽车旅馆。

value.def: If people cluster together, they gather together in a small group.

example.ex: The passengers clustered together in small groups...
example.tran: 乘客们三五成群聚在一起。
孩子们聚集在我的周围。
